    <h3 id="setup">Setup</h3>
    <p>Authorize a user and get access token.</p>
    <blockquote class="code">
      $ bothub configure
    </blockquote>
    <br/>
    <h3 id="project-management">Project management</h3>
    <p>Initialize project on current directory. Create a echo chatbot code.</p>
    <blockquote class="code">
      $ bothub init
    </blockquote>
    <p>Deploy current project.</p>
    <blockquote class="code">
      $ bothub deploy
    </blockquote>
    <p>List of projects.</p>
    <blockquote class="code">
      $ bothub ls
    </blockquote>
    <p>Delete a project.</p>
    <blockquote class="code">
      $ bothub rm &lt;project_name&gt;
    </blockquote>
    <br/>
    <h3 id="channel-management">Channel management</h3>
    <p>List of channels for current project.</p>
    <blockquote class="code">
      $ bothub channel ls
    </blockquote>
    <p>Add a channel for current project.</p>
    <blockquote class="code">
      $ bothub channel add telegram --api-key=&lt;my-api-key&gt;<br/>
      $ bothub channel add facebook --app-id=&lt;app_id&gt; --app-secret=&lt;app_secret&gt; --page-access-token=&lt;page_access_token&gt;
    </blockquote>
    <p>Remove a channel from current project.</p>
    <blockquote class="code">
      $ bothub channel rm &lt;channel&gt;
    </blockquote>
